long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Effortlessly extract and copy keywords and brand names from Google Ads Keyword Planner’s Refine Keywords pane. Simply expand the desired sections, and this extension will compile all the checked keywords into a convenient comma-separated list for easy use.
